N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.3 - Waiting lists

State Regulations

In OGS paid parking facilities where the demand for
parking exceeds the supply of space available, State employees requesting
parking privileges will be placed on a waiting list and assigned space when
available and in accordance with any agreements with recognized employee
organizations. Notes
